title: Seared Chicken, Halloumi & Smokey Capsicum Relish with Garlicky Greens & Lime
description: Bright, bold, and bursting with flavour! This meal pairs juicy, golden chicken with a smokey-sweet relish that takes things up a notch. Served alongside garlicky greens and a zing of fresh lime, it’s a simple yet sensational dish that’s sure to impress!
